org.eclipse.gef4.mvc.models

Class ContentModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.gef4.mvc.models.ContentModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDisposable

    public class ContentModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDisposable
    The ContentModel stores the content Objects that are visualized. The ContentModel fires a property change event when the contents are changed.
